{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01XrqQcVEmmuowNVVXySdhv4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The agent has completed the 4-pass agentic search. Now I need to:\n\n1. Build constraints JSON based on the search results\n2. Self-check constraints\n3. Build answer candidate\n4. Run `spec-anchor realign --answer-json '<json-object>'`\n5. Present the formatted result\n\nLet me build the constraints JSON from the search results:\n\nFrom `#0002-session-management`:\n- Session cookies use secure flags (HttpOnly, Secure)\n- Default timeout is set\n- Session is immediately invalidated on logout\n\n\n- State-changing requests require CSRF token validation\n- Requests missing valid tokens are rejected with 403 Forbidden\n\nNow I'll compile these constraints into JSON and execute the realign command.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2904,"cache_read_input_tokens":24894,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2904},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da","uuid":"b05d82e0-b66f-40d1-ac16-2d0531955abf","request_id":"req_011CbHtuAZfBoPLtqmtwu2mE"}
